The following issues require manual code changes:
  ./ecosystem_grpcreflect_handler.go:10:15: grpcreflect.NewStaticReflector -> grpcreflect.Register(server) serves v1 and v1alpha and lists the server's registered services by default. See docs/v2-migration.md
  ./ecosystem_grpcreflect_handler.go:11:13: grpcreflect.NewHandlerV1 -> grpcreflect.Register(server) serves v1 and v1alpha and lists the server's registered services by default. See docs/v2-migration.md
  ./ecosystem_grpcreflect_handler.go:12:13: grpcreflect.NewHandlerV1Alpha -> grpcreflect.Register(server) serves v1 and v1alpha and lists the server's registered services by default. See docs/v2-migration.md

